item.description:
A couple of years ago a fake sports media company, based in Germany, went after many users on this app for posting short clips of that horrible Australian breakdancer. They were operating in bad faith, and those clips were clearly under the fair use protection of the copyright law. Among other things I decided to write a review of that fake company on Google. Some time ago I got a notification that Google removed that review, but now I checked and it still seems to be there.

---
